        "cooked": "<p>Hi <a href=\"https://forums.foundationdb.org/u/johscheuer\">johscheuer</a>, I also have the similar requirement, I tried to set <code>skip</code> in our cr(fdbcluster) by edit the yaml directly</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-auto\"> oc edit fdbcluster\n  foundationdb_cluster_spec:\n    skip: true\n    databaseConfiguration:\n      logs: 3\n      storage: 4\n</code></pre>\n<p>once save it, check the yaml again using <code>oc get fdbcluster -o yaml</code> the <code>skip:true</code> is gone, it seems it didn\u2019t work, what am I missing? thanks.</p>",
